  "generated_description": "\n    <h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-stone-900 mb-2 font-serif\">The Experience</h3>\n    <p class=\"mb-4 text-stone-600 leading-relaxed\">Borestone is a stunning example of Maine's diverse landscape. You hike through an ancient forest to reach Sunrise Pond, an idyllic alpine tarn, before climbing steep rocks to twin peaks.</p>\n\n    <h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-stone-900 mb-2 font-serif\">The Challenge</h3>\n    <p class=\"mb-4 text-stone-600 leading-relaxed\">The initial approach is a steep access road, followed by a true hiking trail. The final ascent involves rock scrambles and steel handholds.</p>\n\n    <div class=\"bg-emerald-50 border border-emerald-100 p-4 rounded-xl mt-6\">\n        <h4 class=\"text-xs font-bold text-emerald-900 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2\">Local Insight</h4>\n        <p class=\"text-sm text-emerald-800\">There is a small fee for entry as it is an Audubon sanctuary. The visitor center at Sunrise Pond is a great spot to learn about local ecology.</p>\n    </div>\n    ",
